      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MANDELA HAYZE (1) has been mixing form lately, hitting the frame two back before finishing fourth (25.76) at Q Lakeside in a Grade 4/5. Better than latest and can atone here. BROWNLOW (3) was strongly fancied latest and proved too good with a 0.8 lengths win at Q Straight in a handy 18.88. Has a low draw and in form and has the ability. One of main contenders. DO RUN BANDI (7) is worth forgiving for his last effort when fourth (30.49) at this track over 520m. Form at the trip sound including two wins. A forward showing wouldn't surprise. CELTIC GOLD (2) should be in the finish fresh from a 12 weeks break.",
